  "subject": "Restart entire heart beat timer thread",
  "commit_message": "Restart entire heart beat timer thread\n\nCancelling and restarting the timer task caused the scheduler\nto throw an exception, preventing xacml from replying to the\nPDP_UPDATE message, thus causing PAP to remove it from the\nPDP Group.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-2326\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\nChange-Id: I1410cff8b6fb7118151d84d28ecb8a30d58caf27\n",
